{"id":1730470,"retrievedAt":"2026-07-13T13:44:33.307Z","response":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"belongs_to_collection":null,"budget":0,"genres":[],"homepage":"","id":1730470,"imdb_id":null,"origin_country":["US"],"original_language":"en","original_title":"Sayang Tak Dikenang","overview":"# Translation  It tells the story of Ayu Izhani (Ruhainies) and Hattin Isabella (Ezzanie Jasny), two cousins who are close friends despite their families not being close. They study at the same college. After getting jobs, they live in the same rented house. Ayu and Hattin meet the same man but with different names. Raqib Tafzani (Fadlan Hazim) introduces himself as Raqib to Ayu while Hattin knows him as Tafzani. Ayu begins to open her heart to accept Raqib who diligently serves her family. Ayu's mother urges Ayu to accept Raqib as her husband. Hattin receives news that her fiancé, Omar, has been unfaithful with another woman. Worse, Omar becomes hot-tempered and treats Hattin harshly. Hattin keeps this secret from Ayu's knowledge. Tafzani attempts to seduce Hattin after learning that she has broken off her engagement. Hattin begins to be enchanted with feelings of happiness when she is with Tafzani.","popularity":0.0214,"poster_path":"/6ka4UhkaO5yr603SeH03MBo4gig.jpg","production_companies":[{"id":118914,"logo_path":null,"name":"FJ Pictures Sdn Bhd","origin_country":""}],"production_countries":[],"release_date":"2022-01-01","revenue":0,"runtime":0,"softcore":false,"spoken_languages":[],"status":"Released","tagline":"","title":"Sayang Tak Dikenang","video":false,"vote_average":0,"vote_count":0,"alternative_titles":{"titles":[]},"credits":{"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":1321023,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Fadlan Hazim","original_name":"Fadlan Hazim","popularity":0.142,"profile_path":"/v95nQJ029D7EHYsLB0oNRDI2jPE.jpg","cast_id":2,"character":"","credit_id":"6a53955b77b7affc813bbb52","order":0},{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":1742583,"known_for_department":"Ac